text: Lucas Hauchard (born 27 January 1996), also known as Squeezie, is a French YouTuber and Streamer. He is the most well-known French-speaking gamer with over 18.3 million subscribers and 10 billion views. He specialises in Let's Play commentaries and vlogs, and also works with Cyprien Iov on Bigorneaux & Coquillages, a channel with over 6 million subscribers as of October 2019. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:French YouTubers Category:People from Val-de-Marne Category:Living people
